    "review": "We hired The Good DJ Company for our wedding and they were amazing from start to finish. Completely understood the vibe we wanted and the music was what tied the whole event together.\n\nThe booth and decorations were a perfect compliment to the look of the venue and the music really set the tempo of the night. Perfect song choice and kept the dance floor busy the whole time.\n\nThey were also really easy to work with through the whole process and they managed all the setup directly with the vendor, taking a load of stress of our shoulders.\n\nHighly recommend!",
